message.body: good morning. are you still free tonight? it is first friday...
Oh that sounds fun.. I'm coming back to Philly around five, and yes let's go out.
cool.let's plaay it by ear.
Ok, Nate also wants to cook out tonight at his place, we could do that?
cool. i am meeting my friend vincent at 5...will you have ella tonight?
No, she is with Wes' mom
i kinda feel like i should stop into a couple of first friday things bc i never see people and i want to try to network. can i come by after?
I would like to come out for first Friday things as well, we could go over together after?
yay! do you want to be in touch around 7 or 8? i am setting up my new iphone. very exciting.
Oh that is exciting! Welcome to the world of wonder
it is mystical and i am scared of it's power.
That will pass once the mind meld is complete
hey. where you at?
Just got in from school, what are u up to?
home. making some food for pete. what are you feeling like?
I am getting my massage Sunday afternoon, and "maybe" going to a show that night, but do you want company while you pack?
maybe! you going to jess?
Yes, I'm very much looking forward to it!
tell her i say hello!
I will. I'm sorry I'm a flake, the afternoon lecture on grave robbing and 19th century Greek art dealers just took it all out of me. I don't think I'm going to go to Nates either
now i am losing my will....you should watch alphas on netflix.
Whoa, what is that?
That whoa was totally sincere
a cool show. look it up on netflix.
I miss Girls. I will absolutely look it up
Is this a movie or a show?
show
Do you think I had vertigo because I'm am alpha?
yes. it was probably the side effect of your super power.
I gotta just ride it out
whaat is your super power again?
I'm not sure i know
Mind meld is occurring...
So nice to see you....I'm off now...
How was your massage?
I just got out, it was so good! I think she's great, if a little nutty. It was almost two hours!
Isn't she something?
She really is. She was doing a lot of pressure point and organ work. She said she doesn't usually treat a first timer like she treated me, but I'm so "overwhelmed" and a visual person
Ha. Overwhelmed?
Apparently..I've feel great though. It's like some one upped my meds
She is very gifted.
She is. As odd as she is, I'm glad she is in my life : )
I've been 3 times and Pete's been twice... It's Always very mystical.
Did you meet the dog? She always tells me how strong I am.
I feel like I'm living anew. I'm taller. The dog didn't like not know what was going on, so she came in to say hi. Then afterwards she had a piece of pizza
The dog,
Yea the dog. Lucy?
That dog is always a facet.
I didn't know she ate pizza.
She doesn't eat dog food, I was told. Jess heated it up for her.
Have fun and travel safe! I'm glad you are getting a break
